title: John David Souther - Home by Dawn
description:
J.D. Souther was one of the founders of The Souther, Hillman, Furay Band. Of his numerous solo albums, only Home By Dawn has never been issued on CD, until now! It features guest appearances by Linda Ronstadt, Don Henley & Timothy B. Schmit.
